cd82b0c5567ddf2e2c8320befd66","tid":53083,"uid":102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T17:50:02.000Z","msg":"第三季好撚高質"},{"pid":"96c9b9fa4dc9eb0bd3c8efdb68a40b097140c1bc","tid":53083,"uid":11913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-03T15:02:22.000Z","msg":"一次過追哂3季，最尾真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好期待銀魂真人版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e937ebe02d97a0e934cca301d36749a2987839e","tid":53083,"uid":20831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T17:29:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一次過追哂3季，最尾真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好期待銀魂真人版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我又係一口氣追晒3季<br />\n唔知點解覺得木南晴夏第一二季有少少baby fat先cute<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第三季瘦得濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n山田孝之雖然演忠直傻仔但其實睇得出好多地方都有演技<del>忍笑</del> 同埋真係好靚仔<br />\n<br />\n第一季<br />\n最後兩集玩現代世界好好笑 同埋副3D眼鏡最正<br />\n<br />\n第二季<br />\n冇咩印象深刻大爆笑點 但都正<br />\n<br />\n第三季<br />\n喪屍/鬼同玩FF果集笑到有腹肌<br />\n其他唔係好笑得出<br />\n歌舞劇都識笑嘅<br />\n最後eva又係好笑<br />\n同埋打最後boss七條友夾唔啱檔期係用ps整上去好抵死<br />\n我仲以為最後廢柴法師會型返下，點知都係廢到底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}